  author: {
    name: "Sarah thompson",
    avatar: "https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=5"
  },
  date: "December 5, 2021"
}, {
  title: "Building a sustainable future",
  content: "Our reliance on fossil fuels has led to significant environmental and economic challenges. The transition to renewable energy is not just a necessity but an opportunity to create a sustainable and prosperous future.At GreenEnergy, our purpose is to “accelerate the transition to renewable energy.” The urgency to address climate change and energy sustainability has never been more critical. Renewable energy sources, such as solar and wind, offer clean, reliable, and affordable alternatives to fossil fuels.The traditional energy model is heavily dependent on non-renewable resources that contribute to pollution and climate change. To change this, we need to invest in renewable energy infrastructure, promote energy efficiency, and support policies that encourage sustainable practices.Instead of continuing our dependence on fossil fuels, we can choose to transition to renewable energy and build a sustainable future. By doing so, we can protect our environment and create economic opportunities. At GreenEnergy, we are committed to driving this transformation.",
  author: {
    name: "Michael Rodriguez",
    avatar: "https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=11"
  },
  date: "January 20, 2022"
}];
export default blogs;

